alwaysApply: true
description: Protect timing-critical/interrupt code from AI edits
globs:
  - "h5/h5.ino"
rules:
  - match: "/* AI_DO_NOT_MODIFY:"
    action: blockEdits
  - match: "TIMING_CRITICAL"
    action: blockEdits
notes: |
  Only allow edits outside marked blocks. Functions that touch timers, PCNT, ISR, and step pulses must be gated.
